<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="friendship-n">friendship <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'frendʃɪp/    美 /'frendʃɪp/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 友谊；友爱；友情：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>form a friendship 
建立友谊</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>break friendship with 
与…断交</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>May our friendship last till the end of the universe!
愿我们的友谊永存！</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>True friendship is seen through the heart not through the eyes.
真正的友谊不是用眼睛看到的，而是用心体验的。</p></div></div>